{"lastModified":1751538422737,"uri":"c::7819198761::vessel::d5cb5cb4-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744","yachtType":["Motor"],"description":"Operating Area: West Mediterranean\n\nMotoryacht ASLEC 4 Rossinavi a 48-meter semi-displacement characterized by large outdoor spaces and a distinctive straight bow. Steel hull and marine light alloy superstructure. This Rossinavi motoryacht is equipped with two Caterpillar engines of 1,300 hp each that allow it to reach a maximum speed of over 16 knots and a cruising speed at half load of 15 knots. External Design: Studio Spadolini. In addition to the 9 crew members, the ASLEC 4 motoryacht accommodates 10 guests in 5 luxury cabins. The interiors designed by the designer French Remi Tessier have been treated in detail giving ample attention to the choice of materials; Many details have been designed with carbon fibers, precious black chrome and above all by the gold leaf that covers most of the ceilings and walls. A perfect synthesis between luxurious refinement and contemporary allure. Extreme care has also been given to the entertainment on board the Rossinavi, an audio video system with global control extremely intuitive to use. Kaleidescape system for on-demand, Lutron for home automation management and the Apple system with integrated AirPlay for complete audio control.","blueprint":{"name":"ASLEC 4","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cb5cb4-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::eaa5ab80-3b25-11f0-9818-a79e71c43f61/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cb5cb4-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::eaa86aa0-3b25-11f0-826d-8db24f020f53/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cb5cb4-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::eaa891b0-3b25-11f0-9e65-3168e156a159/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cb5cb4-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::eaa36190-3b25-11f0-826d-8db24f020f53/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cb5cb4-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::eaaa6670-3b25-11f0-a841